en: 13th century château. Park, gardens, patio overlooking the Loire River. Heated swimming pool between the garden and vegetable patch. Orangery, restaurant, small Aubusson tapestry room, 16th century stained glass windows. Bedrooms with four-poster beds, marble and wood bathrooms.
fr: Château XIIIe, ancien fief d’Amboise. Parc, jardins, terrasse face à la Loire. Piscine chauffée entre jardin et potager. Orangerie, restaurant, petit salon aux tapisseries Aubusson, vitraux XVIe. Chambres à baldaquin, salles de bain marbre et bois. Chambres duplex au Pavillon Renaissance.
